    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "okay thanks. you mentioned a capacitor... i've seen some videos online about how to swap those out myself. is that a pretty straightforward thing to do once the power is off? like is it just a matter of unplugging the old one and plugging a new one in?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
